Mr Price Says Earnings Per Share to Rise Up to 53% in 53 Weeks to April 2

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-03T06:02:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-03/mr-price-says-earnings-per-share-to-rise-up-to-53-in-53-weeks-to-april-2.html
Mr Price Group Ltd. (MPC)  said basic
earnings per share for the 53 weeks to April 2 are expected to
increase between 48 percent and 53 percent from a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
